Dialogue: 100,0:00:08.35,0:00:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She's introduced me to her parents.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:10.85,0:00:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That means I already hold her heart \Nin the palm of my hand!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:16.60,0:00:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{So now }All that's left...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:19.45,0:00:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is her body!{Unclear italics}
Dialogue: 100,0:00:21.04,0:00:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All that I do, I do for love!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.05,0:00:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.30,0:00:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I put it in.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:31.67,0:00:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually put it in!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:33.42,0:00:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My love potion!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.30,0:00:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, Miss Kobayashi's body will be mine!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:23.12,0:02:25.40,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,Look at that linework!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.40,0:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:27.87,0:02:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much chocolate.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.90,0:02:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's because it's Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.90,0:02:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Valentine's Day?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:34.63,0:02:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a day where you give chocolate to the person you like.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.22,0:02:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, chocolate!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.80,0:02:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:46.90,0:02:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.85,0:02:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy Valentine's!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:49.85,0:02:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, try it.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:55.90,0:02:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:57.15,0:02:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:59.40,0:03:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust is an important concept in this world.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:02.75,0:03:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.75,0:03:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether a relationship is professional or personal,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.86,0:03:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,trust is something that needs to be earned.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.54,0:03:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A single mistake could easily \Ncost someone everything they hold dear.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:17.20,0:03:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it, Tohru?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.75,0:03:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to eat this chocolate now, all right?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:23.34,0:03:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Actually, that one's no good!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm such a lizard-brain.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.70,0:03:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I should head out.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:36.25,0:03:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:39.97,0:03:42.91,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,I even blew a mandrake on that!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:43.65,0:03:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can't let my guard down for a second.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:55.60,0:03:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see the surprise on Shouta{-kun}'s face.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.60,0:04:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:00.76,0:04:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not planning to turn {\i1}yourself{\i0} \Ninto Valentine's chocolate for me, are you?{meh}
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouta{-kun}!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:12.65,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning, Kanna{-san}.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:14.94,0:04:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Saikawa.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.70,0:04:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather's, um... pretty nice today.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.00,0:04:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.30,0:04:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you, um... know what today is?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I do! It's Valentine's Day!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.50,0:04:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually brought some—
Dialogue: 100,0:04:37.70,0:04:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna{-chan}!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.80,0:04:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you friendship chocolate.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.50,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you some, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:45.60,0:04:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.30,0:04:51.68,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,{\i0}I'm{\i1} the one who's supposed to be giving her chocolate right now!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.57,0:04:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kanna{-san}!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:00.43,0:05:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wicked!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.84,0:05:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are yours friendship chocolates, too?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:07.10,0:05:07.83,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,Friendship?{oof}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:07.83,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kanna{-san}, these are...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,r-real...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Saikawa.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.48,0:05:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:18.47,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I eat them now?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.37,0:05:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I suppose.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.35,0:05:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a few minutes before the teacher gets here.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.12,0:05:31.18,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,Licky-lick... Licky-lick... Licky-lick...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.18,0:05:34.43,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,Licky-lick! Licky-lick! Licky-lick!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.86,0:05:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.{meh} My family in Hokkaido sent me a ton of chocolate.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:44.70,0:05:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Valentine's chocolate from your mom?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.05,0:05:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, lay off.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.75,0:05:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Takiya{-kun}, did you get any this year?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I got two.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What a stud.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.45,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Kobayashi{-san}!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamashita{-san} gave me some!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Those chocolates are pretty famous.\NThey're really good.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful holiday this is!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you get chocolate for free!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:13.85,0:06:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi{-san}.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for always helping me out.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.44,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.71,0:06:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you some, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:23.52,0:06:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.77,0:06:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And me.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.60,0:06:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One more.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Another big haul.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:29.76,0:06:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:31.53,0:06:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you getting so much chocolate?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.15,0:06:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks for all her help.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:37.97,0:06:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi{-san} helps out a lot of people around the office.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:42.10,0:06:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thanks for all her help"?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:45.86,0:06:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't worry. I brought some chocolate myself.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:48.71,0:06:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.91,0:06:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,180)}Really? That's unusual.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.90,0:06:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know not to expect much from me.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even think there's enough for everyone.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.81,0:07:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late, Takiya.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.94,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and sit down.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.05,0:07:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.55,0:07:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.40,0:07:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:28.80,0:07:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about that. Just send me the same item.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.02,0:07:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going shopping, \Nso keep an eye on the house.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.48,0:07:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:50.49,0:07:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I want more.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.38,0:07:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.75,0:08:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Tohru?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shopping.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you eating chocolate?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.60,0:08:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, friendship chocolate.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you got friendship chocolate?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.65,0:08:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you {\i1}are{\i0} in elementary school.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want some, too?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.55,0:08:26.15,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,Kanna{-chan}'s eating it, so it should be safe for me, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.65,0:08:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.45,0:08:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum, this is—
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.30,0:08:33.20,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.91,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,What's this? Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:38.25,0:08:39.29,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.16,0:08:43.58,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi, your face is all red.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.45,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,I think I’m getting...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.45,0:08:43.58,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,turned on!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.90,0:08:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a fever?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.15,0:08:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kanna{-chan}! A-About that chocolate...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.35,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I found some that was hidden!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.26,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,I messed up big time!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.55,0:08:53.45,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.45,0:08:56.76,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,I think I'm about to lay my hands on a pure and innocent little girl.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.95,0:09:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna{-chan}, I'm not feeling so great, \Nso I'm going to go lie down.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:02.45,0:09:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:08.06,0:09:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.05,0:09:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you have to do this on Valentine's Day?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.00,0:09:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had any luck with romance, \Nso I just wanted to get through the day peacefully.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.30,0:09:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like last year, quiet... and alone.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:38.35,0:09:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:40.00,0:09:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel all warm inside, almost like I'm...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.45,0:09:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I be...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.81,0:09:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you weren't feeling well. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your weird chocolate...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I ate some of it.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.42,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohru...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat right here.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:09.30,0:10:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.20,0:10:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all wrong.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your maid outfit is all wrong!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.25,0:10:28.15,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,Apparently, some of my chocolate contained alcohol.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.15,0:10:31.36,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,Since it got me drunk, \NI managed to avoid any real problems.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:32.02,0:10:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.30,0:10:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'd be nice if I made some chocolate for everyone.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:48.66,0:10:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I melt this chocolate here...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I do have a lot...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess a little won't hurt.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:01.72,0:11:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.80,0:11:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All done!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:26.99,0:11:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A get-together?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a few days off, \Nso let's have some fun.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:31.85,0:11:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good. Where are we going?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:34.80,0:11:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the hot springs?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:38.70,0:11:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I've been to a hot spring.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:41.18,0:11:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:42.38,0:11:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can never bring \Nmyself to go alone.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Would anybody like any refreshments?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:48.93,0:11:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have one of each bento box.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:50.90,0:11:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With pleasure.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi, ice cream! For Saikawa, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:54.80,0:11:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:55.96,0:11:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouta{-kun}, is there anything you want?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:00.10,0:12:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't accept gifts from demons!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:06.50,0:12:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Four coffees for us, please.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:08.60,0:12:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming right up.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:11.28,0:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, could you make one of those... an apple juice?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:18.09,0:12:21.50,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we're actually going on a hot springs trip like this.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:21.50,0:12:25.15,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,A new environment with a fresh atmosphere.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:25.15,0:12:27.55,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,It's the perfect situation for {\i0}this{\i1}.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:27.55,0:12:30.52,Default - Italic,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll show her my love for sure!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:39.53,0:12:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi, what is this place?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:41.85,0:12:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hot springs village.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little cold.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:44.70,0:12:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of strange seeing so much snow piled up here.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:47.85,0:12:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna{-san}, let's go check that out.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:50.37,0:12:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the hot spring manju?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:54.64,0:12:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Fafnir{-san}. We're moving on.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:57.55,0:12:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:00.30,0:13:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a lot more sociable than I expected.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:04.60,0:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons fundamentally have more freedom.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:09.30,0:13:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all about power.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:10.75,0:13:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Socializing with humans, \N{interacting with and }taking part in your culture.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:13.89,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Our power affords us the freedom to do so.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:16.15,0:13:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The stronger you are, \Nthe more you're free to act on your whims.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:19.55,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we expect this whimsy to continue?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:30.30,0:13:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is great!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We lucked out.\NA big party just cancelled.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:38.88,0:13:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry to have kept you waiting. \NYou're Mr. Takiya{-sama}, yes?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please follow me.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:48.15,0:13:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at her on her knees in front of us.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:50.14,0:13:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be able to sense my magnificent aura.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:53.60,0:13:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:55.27,0:13:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just a Japanese maid's hospitality.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hospitality?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:01.10,0:14:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be able to learn a thing or two \Nwhile we're here, so pay close attention.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:05.45,0:14:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I'm far more impressive than they are.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:07.80,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, what could I possibly learn from a lowly human?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:11.05,0:14:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:12.55,0:14:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I like Kanna{-chan} the best.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:35.16,0:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, Kanna{-san}...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to... wash your back now.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:41.35,0:14:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Saikawa.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:47.32,0:14:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I've got a question.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:49.79,0:14:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:50.57,0:14:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you guys all look the way you do?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:54.70,0:14:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think, like, "I want to be cute!" and stuff when you transform?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:59.46,0:15:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my natural form.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:01.55,0:15:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to explain.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:04.35,0:15:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohru{-kun} uses magic to transform her physical body.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:07.85,0:15:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This process doesn't change her Idea, \Nit simply alters Tohru's substance
Dialogue: 100,0:15:12.20,0:15:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,from a dragon form into an equivalent human form.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"Idea"?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing Plato talked about?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:20.31,0:15:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:22.81,0:15:26.67,Default,,0,0,25,,{\q2}By dragon standards, you're all good-looking with nice figures,
Dialogue: 100,0:15:26.67,0:15:29.49,Default,,0,0,25,,so your human forms match that.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what she meant by "natural form"?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:31.82,0:15:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nailed it.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:33.37,0:15:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what I'd look like as{if I turned into} a dragon.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:36.99,0:15:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Roar!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:38.34,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's my face the same?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the lack of back problems, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:42.37,0:15:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Roar!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:43.30,0:15:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just your stomach talking, isn't it?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:45.63,0:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Roar!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:46.84,0:15:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:47.96,0:15:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that you're great just the way you are.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:53.05,0:15:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like they're having fun over there.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:56.05,0:15:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you want to go on this trip with everyone?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:59.57,0:16:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:01.72,0:16:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Something big happened not too long ago, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:05.32,0:16:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were looking out for us.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a real nuisance.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:11.00,0:16:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you stand to gain from this?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:13.50,0:16:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your goal?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Community.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:18.50,0:16:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a group of friends who all get along, \Nand sometimes I get to join in with them.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:23.75,0:16:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I'm actually with them or just watching, I'm having fun.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:28.15,0:16:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how kids these days think, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:31.02,0:16:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And just so you know, Faf{-kun}, \Nyou're part of that group.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:37.60,0:16:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you, Takiya.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:40.47,0:16:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a tsundere!{characterization is a wonderful thing}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That was great.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:47.26,0:16:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:48.60,0:16:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the fabled "drink after a bath," huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:53.99,0:16:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouta{-kun}, what are you looking at?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:56.16,0:16:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A sword?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:57.10,0:16:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a keychain.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:59.40,0:17:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys really can't get enough of that stuff.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:03.23,0:17:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want it?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't need it!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:05.65,0:17:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just looking around{browsing}.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:11.58,0:17:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouta{-kun}.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, a present.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:18.55,0:17:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I like this kind of stuff, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:25.98,0:17:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally time for us to settle our score.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:30.10,0:17:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready to cry when I beat you.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi, witness me!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:34.76,0:17:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:37.53,0:17:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even see it.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:38.50,0:17:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Subjects!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:39.07,0:17:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Suck.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:40.41,0:17:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyami-nyami!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:40.99,0:17:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Reigns supreme.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:41.99,0:17:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaboom!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:43.70,0:17:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck is this?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:49.25,0:17:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this is more like it.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:51.00,0:17:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we're up next.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:53.90,0:17:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like where this is going, \Nso you don't get a turn.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I'm pretty beat after all that.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I might hop into the hot spring again.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:06.98,0:18:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:13.32,0:18:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fun day.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:16.11,0:18:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This world's hot springs sure are fun.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:20.00,0:18:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to \Neven more great food tomorrow.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice and warm.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:29.12,0:18:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:30.54,0:18:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, you can take the day off from being my maid.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:36.40,0:18:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your personal maid,\N7 days a week, 365 days a year.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:40.39,0:18:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me to stop.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:42.00,0:18:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:50.25,0:18:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:54.55,0:18:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Could we go for a little walk outside?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:59.30,0:19:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:15.42,0:19:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Brrr! It's colder than I expected.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I put up a barrier?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:19.85,0:19:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. It's not that bad.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:26.85,0:19:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:29.94,0:19:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, take this!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:33.73,0:19:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's normal chocolate!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:54.80,0:19:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate, huh? Thanks for this.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:07.50,0:20:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "Chocolate, huh?"{punctuation is a no-win situation with this phrasing}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you know what I meant.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:17.06,0:20:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:17.85,0:20:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:19.15,0:20:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to great lengths to ensure its deliciousness!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:22.03,0:20:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, within human lengths, of course.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:25.50,0:20:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:26.85,0:20:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:37.90,0:20:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready to head back?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:40.67,0:20:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:44.30,0:20:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Miss Kobayashi, \Nshall we procreate before we return?{( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°)}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:48.01,0:20:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But the mood's perfect!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:49.35,0:20:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What mood? Besides, you're not\Nsupposed to say that stuff out loud.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:52.64,0:20:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. In that case, \Nlet's stop talking and just do it!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:55.25,0:20:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:08.30,0:21:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's asleep.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:10.00,0:21:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They were enjoying themselves the whole time.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:12.60,0:21:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they'd be tired.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:15.60,0:21:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That really was a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:19.65,0:21:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Takiya{-kun}, thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:21.75,0:21:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:22.76,0:21:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on the same team, aren't we?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:24.95,0:21:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As coworkers?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:27.10,0:21:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As friends.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:32.72,0:21:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.{>_>}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:34.23,0:21:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:35.55,0:21:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been eating the whole time, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:38.50,0:21:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was nowhere near enough.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:40.15,0:21:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Elma, could you please keep it down?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:42.45,0:21:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Your voice is annoying.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:43.99,0:21:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:44.86,0:21:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a problem?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:46.55,0:21:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. No fighting, you two.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They've still got energy to spare.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to fight, fight outside.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:53.65,0:21:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:54.70,0:21:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Elma, let's take this outside.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:56.71,0:21:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Bring it on.
