Comment: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:09.46,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}Tell me, how did I get here?
Comment: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:11.42,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}I only made one tiny-winey mistake
Comment: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:15.13,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}and now I'm at a ta-la-la ta-la-ta total loss
Comment: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:16.63,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}Why now of all times
Comment: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:18.43,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}did I grow a spine and stick around?
Comment: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:21.97,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}Somehow I've been taken by whimsy
Comment: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:24.22,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}with no choice but to sing along
Comment: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:27.56,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}That's just how it is at first,
Comment: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:31.23,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}feeling like you're not in control
Comment: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:34.78,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}But if you open up and listen...
Comment: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:39.91,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}that's your voice saying, "Come on! Let's go!"
Comment: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:41.66,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}(Anywhere is fine!)
Comment: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:48.54,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}I have the courage to become your wings
Comment: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:52.09,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}I'll take on the world without any fear
Comment: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:56.01,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}as long as I feel this magic
Comment: 0,0:01:56.01,0:02:02.80,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}A bouquet for this unfamiliar world,
Comment: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:06.68,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}wrapped up together in this moment
Comment: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:08.35,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}We communicate on different levels,
Comment: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:10.23,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}but it doesn't bother me one bit
Comment: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:12.65,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}so long as this peace lasts forevermore
