Comment: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:26.28,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\an5\move(960,162,960,-316,2030,2330)\c&H23AAFF&}and give my all to serve you
Comment: 0,0:22:26.03,0:22:28.37,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\an5\move(960,1284,960,162,0,310)\c&HEBAFE9&}We'll spend all our time together,
