Comment: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:34.95,ED-E,clipout,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&H9B48B8&}Pure bliss~ {_ln choose the punctuation}{tildes cuz Tohru's a huge weeb}{ln you clown this is elma} Seconds, please!
Comment: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:37.25,ED-E,clipin,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&HF7CD89&}Come on, snuggle with me
Comment: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:41.34,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&HF7CD89&}Get over here and quit being a tease!
Comment: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:43.80,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&HEBAFE9&}Why must the rules be so strict?
Comment: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:46.01,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&HF7CD89&}It's like my heart's bound in chains
Comment: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:50.47,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,What an inferior and foolish system of values
Comment: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:52.68,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&H9B48B8&}It just isn't any good
Comment: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:54.64,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&H23AAFF&}These "morals" of yours are worthless
Comment: 0,0:22:54.64,0:22:58.48,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&H23AAFF&}Ah~ I wanna eradicate it all!
Comment: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:04.03,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,Let's do some interspecies communication
Comment: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:08.28,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,and eclipse the world with our passion
Comment: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:12.91,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,A whole week of that?
Comment: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:17.50,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,It'd be more precious than an eternity
Comment: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:20.92,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,The past and the future don't mean a thing
Comment: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:23.04,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,Simply being here right now
Comment: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:25.30,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,with the people here right now
Comment: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:26.26,ED-E,nooffset,0,0,0,karaoke,is what I love!
Comment: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:30.64,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,interspecies communication
Comment: 0,0:23:32.85,0:23:35.02,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,supersimple imagination
Comment: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:39.98,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,Eliminate common sense and you're in paradise! Paradise!
